{"componentChunkName":"component---src-layouts-blog-post-layout-js","path":"/blog/how-to-rename-carts-page-checkout-button","result":{"pageContext":{"id":354,"date":"2021-01-31T13:56:15","date_gmt":"2021-01-31T13:56:15","guid":{"rendered":"https://www.ezfy.club/?p=354"},"modified":"2021-01-31T14:01:22","modified_gmt":"2021-01-31T14:01:22","slug":"how-to-rename-carts-page-checkout-button","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https://www.ezfy.club/how-to-rename-carts-page-checkout-button/","title":{"rendered":"How to rename the cart&#8217;s page checkout button on your Shopify theme"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>By default, every Debut theme comes with the checkout button&#8217;s text of &#8220;check out&#8221;. However, it&#8217;s very simple to change it.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Locating the checkout&#8217;s button text</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>In your Shopify Admin go to: <strong>online store > themes > actions > edit language</strong>s<br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1081\" height=\"779\" class=\"wp-image-357\" style=\"width: 400px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/inline-image.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/inline-image.jpg 1081w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/inline-image-600x432.jpg 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/inline-image-768x553.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1081px) 100vw, 1081px\" /><br></li><li>On the new page that opens up, at the top, click on &#8220;cart&#8221;. It should be the third item of the menu.</li><li>Scroll down until you find the text &#8220;Checkout&#8221; with a textbox below it. You can now edit it as per your wish.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"743\" height=\"625\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/checkout-123.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-359\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/checkout-123.jpg 743w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/checkout-123-600x505.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 743px) 100vw, 743px\" /></figure>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Find out how to rename your cart&#8217;s page button text to freely A/B test what works better.</p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":366,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[9],"tags":[154],"image_alt":"","acf":[],"featured_image_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Debut-Slider-Pro-4-600x338.png","featured_image_small_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Debut-Slider-Pro-4-100x100.png","featured_image_large_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Debut-Slider-Pro-4-1200x675.png","post_count":0,"categories_names":["Blog"],"tag_names":["Code Tutorial"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/354"}],"collection":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/types/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/users/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/comments?post=354"}],"version-history":[{"count":2,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/354/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":368,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/354/revisions/368"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/media/366"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/media?parent=354"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/categories?post=354"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/tags?post=354"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https://api.w.org/{rel}","templated":true}]}}},"staticQueryHashes":["1739988571","1995349551"]}